 new and improved protocols to deliver better connectivity and performance for your apps. In this first of two sessions, we’ll cover ECN, IPv6, Network Extensions, and Multipath protocols."}],"url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc17-707-advances-in-networking-part-1","kind":"article","type":"topic","title":"Advances in Networking, Part 1"},"https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2015/719":{"checksum":null,"type":"download","url":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/videos\/play\/wwdc2015\/719","identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/videos\/play\/wwdc2015\/719"},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC15":{"title":"WWDC15","abstract":[{"text":"Xcode 7, Swift 2.0, iOS 9, macOS 10.11 (El Capitan), watchOS 2.","type":"text"}],"kind":"article","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC15","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"WWDC15-Icon.png"},{"type":"card","identifier":"WWDC15.jpeg"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc15","role":"collectionGroup"},"WWDCNotes.png":{"identifier":"WWDCNotes.png","alt":null,"type":"image","variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDCNotes.png"}]},"WWDC15-Icon.png":{"alt":null,"type":"image","variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC15-Icon.png"}],"identifier":"WWDC15-Icon.png"}}}